18. Risks
Risk	Mitigation
Real mesh networking complexity	Simulate relay
Time limitation	Focus on UI + flow
API delays	Use mock data
Battery drain	Simulate optimization
19. Competitive Advantage
Existing Apps	ResQMesh
Internet dependent	Offline-first
No AI prioritization	AI emergency analysis
No mesh relay	Device relay concept
Limited local coordination	Community resource sharing
20. Future Scope
Real decentralized networking
Government disaster integration
Satellite communication
Drone relay
IoT sensors
Predictive AI disaster analysis
Wearable integration
21. Pitch Summary

“ResQMesh transforms smartphones into a decentralized emergency communication network. During disasters when internet infrastructure fails, nearby devices relay SOS messages offline until rescue teams receive them. AI prioritizes emergencies, coordinates volunteers, and helps save lives faster.”